<h3>Travel to Baltimore</h3>
<p>
    We recommend that you fly into Baltimore-Washington International (BWI) Airport, though it is possible to come into Philadelphia 
    (PHL), Dulles (IAD), or Reagan National (DCA) Airports. If you fly to BWI, you may take the 
    <%= link_to('SuperShuttle', 'http://www.bwiairport.com/en/travel/ground-transportation/trans/supershuttle') %>
    (1800-BLUE-VAN / 1800-258-3826) to Radisson Cross-Keys.
</p>
<p>Directions to the Radisson Hotel at Cross Keys (by car; there is free parking at the hotel if you want to rent a car)</p>

<div style="overflow:auto;">
    <div style="float:left;">
    <h4>All Points North</h4>	    
        <ul>
            <li>Access I-95 southbound from NY, NJ or Philadelphia</li>
            <li>Follow I-95 to I-695 towards Towson </li>
            <li>Take I-695 to exit 23 ( I-83 South )</li>
            <li>Take I-83 to exit 10A Northern Parkway East</li>
            <li>Make a left off the ramp (EAST)</li>
            <li>Once on Northern Parkway take a right onto Falls Rd.(first light)</li>
            <li>Make a right at the first light into the Village of Cross Keys</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>All Points South</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Access I-95 northbound</li>
            <li>Follow I-95 to I-395 towards Downtown Baltimore</li>
            <li>Take I-395 to Pratt St.(3rd light), make a right</li>
            <li>Take Pratt to President St and make a left</li>
            <li>President will turn into I-83 north</li>
            <li>Take I-83 to exit 10A Northern Parkway East</li>
            <li>Once on Northern Parkway make a right onto Falls Rd.(first light)</li>
            <li>Make a right at the first light into the Village of Cross Keys</li>
        </ul>
