        <h4>BWI to the Radisson</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>From the airport follow I-295 towards Baltimore</li>
            <li>Proceed on I-295 into Baltimore and turn right onto Pratt St.</li>
            <li>Take Pratt to President St and make a left on President St.</li>
            <li>President turns into I-83 north</li>
            <li>Take I-83 to exit 10A Northern Parkway East</li>
            <li>Once on Northern Parkway make a right onto Falls Rd.(first light)</li>
            <li>Make a right at the first light into the Village of Cross Keys</li>
        </ul>
